[5.817992, "o", "## Semantic Search Results\r\n\r\n**Result 1:**\r\n\r\n**Score:** 0.56\r\n\r\n\u001b[1mClaude\u001b[22m \u001b[1mDesktop\u001b[22m\r\n\r\nConf\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mg f\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mle:\r\n\r\n- macOS — `~/L\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mbrary/Appl\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mcat\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mon Support/\u001b[1mClaude\u001b[22m/\u001b[1mclaude\u001b[22m_\u001b[1mdesktop\u001b[22m_conf\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mg.json`\r\n- W\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mn\u001b[1mdo\u001b[22mws — `%APPDATA%\\\u001b[1mClaude\u001b[22m\\\u001b[1mclaude\u001b[22m_\u001b[1mdesktop\u001b[22m_conf\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mg.json`\r\n\r\nAdd to \u001b[1mthe\u001b[22m `mcp\u001b[1mServer\u001b[22ms` object (Ollama prov\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mder s\u001b[1mhow\u001b[22mn):\r\n\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n  \"mcp\u001b[1mServer\u001b[22ms\": {\r\n    \"knowledge-base\": {\r\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\r\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@jean\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mbarz/knowledge-base-mcp-\u001b[1mserver\u001b[22m\"],\r\n      \"env\": {\r\n        \"KNOWLEDGE_BASES_ROOT_D\u001b[1mI\u001b[22mR\": \"<KB_ROOT>\",\r\n        \"EMBEDD\u001b[1mI\u001b[22mNG_PROV\u001b[1mI\u001b[22mDER\": \"ollama\",\r\n        \"OLLAMA_BASE_URL\": \"http://localhost:11434\",\r\n        \"OLLAMA_MODEL\": \"dengcao/Qwen3-Embedd\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mng-0.6B:Q8_0\"\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nRestart \u001b[1mClaude\u001b[22m \u001b[1mDesktop\u001b[22m after ed\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mt\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mng \u001b[1mthe\u001b[22m f\u001b[1mi\u001b[22mle. \u001b[1mThe\u001b[22m \u001b[1mserver\u001b[22m appears \u001b[1mi\u001b[22mn \u001b[1mthe\u001b[22m tools menu once \u001b[1mthe\u001b[22m handshake succeeds.\r\n\r\n**Source:** [project-docs/clients.md#L52-L78](kb://project-docs/clients.md#L52-L78)\r\n\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n  \"chunkIndex\": 6,\r\n  \"extension\": \".md\",\r\n  \"knowledgeBase\": \"project-docs\",\r\n  \"loc\": {\r\n    \"lines\": {\r\n      \"from\": 52,\r\n      \"to\": 78\r\n    }\r\n  },\r\n  \"relativePath\": \"project-docs/clients.md\",\r\n  \"source\": \"/tmp/kb-demo/knowledge_bases/project-docs/clients.md\",\r\n  \"tags\": [],\r\n  \"injection_signals\": []\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n> **Disclaimer:** The provided results might not all be relevant. Please cross-check the relevance of the information.\r\n\r\n> _Index up-to-date as of 2026-06-10T22:00:32.354Z._\r\n"]
